
	
          Park Group Plc - Our Products












“The UK’s leading multi-redemption voucher and prepaid gift card business”HomeAbout UsOur BusinessesOur BrandsOur ProductsInvestorsContact Us

 
          Our ProductsLove2shop voucherThe Love2shop voucher is the UK’s leading multi-retailer gift voucher with billings in the year to 31 March 2015 running at circa £322million.  It is accepted by over 140 major retailers with more than 20,000 branches.  This means you don’t have to worry about your recipient’s personal tastes – they have the freedom of the high street. The Love2shop Euro voucher was launched in 2011 and is accepted in Ireland by an ever increasing range of retailers now totalling 43.  Love2shop gift cardThe Love2shop gift card is the gift card alternative to the UK’s leading multi-retailer paper voucher.  Once activated, the card can be spent instantly as full or part payment in a fantastic range of major stores.The card is powered by our secure, in-house flexecash® platform, and with no set up fees, load fees, annual maintenance charges or management fees, it offers significant savings compared to other pre-paid multi-option cards.  Cards can be sent out live or inactive and all cards can be reloaded.  This facility is provided by Park Card Services Ltd who are authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority to issue electronic money. Love2shop Extra gift cardThe Love2shop Extra (formerly Love2choose) gift card allows you to provide an unrivalled recognition scheme to your employees and customers with a pre-paid gift card that puts them in the driving seat.  Built on the same flexecash® platform as the Love2shop gift card, it offers instant in-store spending power.  Recipients can also choose to ‘swap’ the value on their card for gift cards and vouchers from a wide range of additional retailers. Love2shop Holidays cardThe Love2shop Holidays (formerly Love2travel) gift card provides access to an ATOL bonded travel agency for all holiday and travel requirements.  It takes the hassle out of organising travel incentives and allows your recipients to be in control of where they want to go.  For an extra personal touch we can even personalise gift cards and carriers to reflect your company’s branding.The card gives access to over 200 travel companies and can be used towards package holidays, UK breaks and theme parks, flights, cruises, hotels, car hire, airport parking, insurance and much more. Client branded cardsLove2shop gift cards can be personalised to reflect corporate identity or campaign theme.  Inline with other pre-paid multi-option cards on the market, we can restrict the number of redeemers on the card, for example restricting the card to clothing retailers only. Retailer vouchersIn addition to the Love2shop gift voucher and gift card we also offer a wide range of retailer vouchers and cards via Love2reward.co.uk and highstreetvouchers.com.  Our Love2shop Extra gift card can also be used to buy other retailer vouchers. Hampers, gifts & experiencesBoth our corporate and consumer businesses offer a wide range of hampers, gifts and experiences in addition to our voucher and card products.© Park Group plc 2011 
