Coats plc









We manufacture the world‘s threads and yarns
– for over 250 years we‘ve helped to connect and form the fabric of daily life on our planet


Learn more about Coats








As firefighters go about their work
our performance threads and zips offer heat and flame protection at temperatures up to 370°C


Our Industrial threads


Our creative teams take influences
from the world‘s people, places, cultures and customs to develop rich pattern collections that inspire and delight


Our Crafts brands


At the extremes of human performance
our high tensile industrial threads and yarns provide strength and flexibility when it matters


Our technical threads


In our long history of pioneering we like to include
Thomas Edison who used Coats thread in his
experiments to perfect the lightbulb


Our heritage


Because we were one of the world‘s first truly
multi-national organisations there are over 60 countries that we call home


Our communities


We manufacture the world‘s threads and yarns
– for over 250 years we‘ve helped to connect and form the fabric of daily life on our planet


Learn more about Coats







				 
			

				 
			

				 
			

				 
			

				 
			

				 
			







 
 
 
 
 
 


















